```csharp
mysqldump -u username -p original_database > backup_file.sql
mysql -u username -p -h target_database_server new_database < backup_file.sql
```

Replace "username" with the MySQL username you want to use, "original\_database" with the name of the original database, "target\_database\_server" with the name or IP address of the target database server, and "new\_database" with the name of the new database you created in step 2.
